# Your First Jaringan Page

## Basic Structure

A Jaringan page is plain text with special syntax:

```
# Page Title

Paragraph content goes here.

=> link-target Link Label
```

## Viewing Your Page

```
jaringan-browser open my-page.jrg
```

Or serve a directory:

```
jaringan-browser serve . 127.0.0.1:7070
```

Then connect from another terminal:

```
jaringan-browser get jrg://127.0.0.1:7070/my-page.jrg
```

